  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Children with Learning Difficulties in Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">At Backup Uganda, we focus on giving learners the attention and instruction that best suit their learning needs. In Uganda, it is not yet a priority to meet the needs of learners with learning difficulties. With class sizes upwards of 70 children, struggling learners are overlooked and pushed along in their education. We empower their teachers and parents to identify their difficulties and work with them in order to prevent dropping out of school or getting lost in the system.</narrative>
  </description>
